oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Split Fountain Printing; Phillips, Sam, 1923-2003; Country Music Hall of Fame & Museum (Nashville, Tenn.);Exhibitions; Woodcuts (prints); Autographs;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black and gold on split fountain, purple to blue) Hatch poster announcing Flyin' Saucers Rock and Roll The Cosmic Genius of Sam Phillips exhibit at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum open from August 2015 to June 2016. Poster features woodcuts of an alien space ship, stars, and flowers. Poster is signed by artists.
